Hemispher

DATA  %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(x = Hemisphere, y = HappinessScore, fill = Hemisphere),
               alpha = 0.5,outlier.colour = "red") +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_bw()  + 
  xlab("")

Region

DATA  %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(x = Region, y = HappinessScore, fill = Region),

  coord_flip() +
  theme_bw()  + 
  xlab("")

Hemisphere 

DATA %>%
  filter(Hemisphere == 'both') %>%
  group_by(Region) %>%
  summarise(Mean = mean(HappinessScore)) %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_bar(aes(x = Region,  y = round(Mean,2),fill = Region),stat = 'identity') +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom") +
  ylab("HappinessScore")

DATA %>%
  filter(Hemisphere == 'north') %>%
  group_by(Region) %>%
  summarise(Mean = mean(HappinessScore)) %>%
  ggplot() +

  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom") +

    ylab("HappinessScore")

# Happiness, Hemisphere
DATA %>%
  group_by(Hemisphere) %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_boxplot(aes(x = Hemisphere, y = HappinessScore ,fill = Hemisphere)) +
  theme_bw()

ANOVA = aov(HappinessScore ~ Hemisphere, data = DATA)
summary(ANOVA)
##              Df Sum Sq Mean Sq F value Pr(>F)  
## Hemisphere    2   8.15   4.076   3.201 0.0443 *
## Residuals   119 151.52   1.273                 
## ---
## Signif. codes:  0 '***' 0.001 '**' 0.01 '*' 0.05 '.' 0.1 ' ' 1
ggplot(DATA) +
  geom_point(aes(x = Beer_PerCapita + Wine_PerCapita, y = HappinessScore, col = Hemisphere)) +
  geom_smooth(aes(x = Beer_PerCapita + Wine_PerCapita, y = HappinessScore, col = Hemisphere),method = 'lm') +
  theme_bw()

DATA$Alchol = DATA$Beer_PerCapita + DATA$Wine_PerCapita
#  
cor(DATA$Alchol,DATA$HappinessScore)
## [1] 0.5511481
DATA2 = DATA %>%
  filter(Hemisphere == "both")
cor(DATA2$Alchol,DATA2$HappinessScore)
## [1] 0.9164067
DATA3 = DATA %>%
  filter(Hemisphere == "north")
cor(DATA3$Alchol,DATA3$HappinessScore)
## [1] 0.549504
DATA4 = DATA %>%
  filter(Hemisphere == "south")
cor(DATA4$Alchol,DATA4$HappinessScore)
## [1] 0.667591

Data3 => north Correlation Data4 => south Correlation
